WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:06.000
A sailboat eases away from the wooden docks of the marina, its white sail already hoisted.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
A volunteer in a blue vest stands on the finger dock and waves as the boat slips past.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Rows of moored boats and tall masts glide by on the left.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:30.000
In the cockpit, two crew members in sun hats and vests settle in near the winches.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:36.000
The boat clears the fairway and turns toward open water.
